        <h5 class="alert-heading"><b>Whoa!</b></h5>
        <p class="mb-0" style="font-size: 15px;">Hey there! You seem to have JavaScript disabled. This sites runs heavily on JavaScript, so please enable JavaScript or uprgrade to a newer version of your browser. Thank you!</p>
